trans-unit.source: Represents a container that holds the contents of a templated menu item in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: 表示保留中範本化功能表項目的內容的容器<xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref>控制項。

trans-unit.source: The MenuItemTemplateContainer class is used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control as a container for the contents of the menu items that are rendered using a custom template.
trans-unit.target: MenuItemTemplateContainer 類別會由<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>做為使用自訂範本轉譯的功能表項目內容的容器控制項。</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This class is used by control developers primarily when extending the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> class to create a container for a templated menu item.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > 這個類別由控制項開發人員主要用於當擴充<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>類別建立樣板化的功能表項目的容器。</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.source: You can define a custom template for the dynamic and static menu items of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DynamicItemTemplate%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticItemTemplate%2A> properties, respectively.
trans-unit.target: 您可以定義自訂的動態和靜態功能表項目範本<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>控制項使用<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DynamicItemTemplate%2A>和<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticItemTemplate%2A>屬性，分別。</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticItemTemplate%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DynamicItemTemplate%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.source: For a list of initial property values for an instance of the MenuItemTemplateContainer class, see the MenuItemTemplateContainer constructor.
trans-unit.target: 如需 MenuItemTemplateContainer 類別的執行個體的初始屬性值的清單，請參閱 MenuItemTemplateContainer 建構函式。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemTemplateContainer"></xref> class using the specified menu item index and menu item.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemTemplateContainer"></xref>類別使用指定的功能表項目索引和功能表項目。

trans-unit.source: Use this constructor to create a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemTemplateContainer> class using the specified menu item index and menu item.
trans-unit.target: 使用這個建構函式建立的新執行個體<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemTemplateContainer>類別使用指定的功能表項目索引和功能表項目。</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemTemplateContainer>
